Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.30,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\frz349\frx0\fry12\pos(1169.6,630)}模型台解说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.30,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\frz355.6\frx2\fry14\pos(1272,810.8)}化石鉴赏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.30,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\frx0\fry12\frz359.4\pos(1177.6,978.8)}研磨纺锤虫体验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,事先虽然想到过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但没想到要开始地质勘探的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,费用和手续都很复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:13.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,采集到的岩土芯  学校可能会保存着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学校好像只有纸质资料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个像胶带纸一样  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地质勘探结果就是这样写的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,新谷老师  有琼脂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:34.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:41.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,模拟地质勘探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:47.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对了  在咖啡店里提供这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.26,Asteroid - HandWrite2,,0,0,0,,{\frz350.3\pos(1611.2,492.4)}地质勘探果冻
